counting-out pen
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a pen where sheep are held after shearing, crutching, dipping or drafting, where they can be tallied for payment purposes.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
